findings.title: Deployer cannot mint after initial deployment
findings.description: The deployer of the contract loses the ability to mint new tokens after the initial deployment.

findings.title: Deployer cannot pause/lock the contract
findings.description: The deployer does not have the capability to pause or lock the contract.

findings.title: Deployer cannot set max transaction limit
findings.description: The deployer does not have the capability to set a maximum transaction limit.

findings.title: Deployer cannot burn tokens
findings.description: The deployer does not have the capability to burn tokens.

findings.title: Deployer cannot set and modify taxes/fees
findings.description: The deployer of the contract does not have the capability to set or modify taxes and fees.

findings.title: Contract has a rebase variable
findings.description: The contract contains a rebase variable which can potentially lead to unintended behavior or manipulation.
